UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Just as I suspected.$B$BMost of the empire has remained closed off since Krik''thir''s final stand. Perhaps my people have already secured the depths and merely await release? Perhaps the faceless ones fester behind closed doors.$B$BOnly time will tell. The exposed upper reaches of Azjol-Nerub must first be cleansed of Arthas'' taint.' WHERE `Id`=29811; -- The Gatewatcher's Talisman
