UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I was wondering if those two would come in handy. They''ve seemed quite out of place ever since they arrived.$B$BI saw Ricket around here just a moment ago. I''ll gladly send her back through the portal with you. She''s less likely to be blowing up any local plant life on that side of things anyway.$B$BLet''s see... where is she...' WHERE `Id`=29281; -- Additional Armaments
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hey you! Good to see you again!$B$BI''m settled in good and fine, actually! It''s good to be with good old Damek again. I never thought I''d be mixing with a dwarf so well, but he and I, we''ve got like minds on all the important stuff.$B$BYou go do your thing. Don''t be worrying about us. If we cook up any good toys for you, we''ll be sure to let ya know!' WHERE `Id`=29282; -- Well Armed
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You killed him?  We have been trying to take that guy out for weeks!  We thank you, $n.' WHERE `Id`=28682; -- Claiming The Keep
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is GREAT! You did it!$b$bThanks, $gmister:miss;!' WHERE `Id`=29412; -- Blown Away
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Oh, I do smell something tasty!  I hope you gave that bird quite a good beating.$b$bPlease, help yourself to some of my extra stock.  I''m sure someone of your talent could put it to good use.' WHERE `Id`=11377; -- Revenge is Tasty
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nice work on the undead up there $n.  We really appreciate the help.' WHERE `Id`=28679; -- Rattling Their Cages
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I am impressed, $c. Your deeds will be remembered among the Shadow Wardens.' WHERE `Id`=29192; -- The Wardens are Watching
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You must be quite the swimmer... all I can manage is the dead man''s float.$B$BIn any case, excellent batch of snails you''ve gathered. Thank you.' WHERE `Id`=29333; -- Escargot A Go-Go
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The dead feed the flies.  The flies feed the spiders.  The spiders feed the frogs.  The frogs feed our moat monster... It''s a beautiful circle of life with the goal of ending life.' WHERE `Id`=29361; -- Moat Monster!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I understand. We are prepared. We shall join the march and meet you on the far side of the portal.' WHERE `Id`=29283; -- Calling the Ancients
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You chose a wise time to call upon us, $c. I was concerned for our ability to stand against the elements in this realm, but the protection of the Sentinel Tree has proven far more than sufficient shelter.$B$BWe will do anything we can to aid your efforts here. Witherbranch has met with your other allies and is discussing a way to corner some of Ragnaros'' lieutenants. You should speak with them when the time comes.' WHERE `Id`=29284; -- Aid of the Ancients
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Lord Torvos accepts the plans and looks over them.>$B$BYou''ve done the offensive a great service, $N, but we should not rest. I wouldn''t put it beyond our foes to plan more mischief in the future.' WHERE `Id`=11877; -- Sunfury Attack Plans
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nice work $N!  I will see that these rations are returned to the troops immediately.' WHERE `Id`=26235; -- Even Thieves Get Hungry
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can''t make any promises, $N.  But I will try my best to purify these.' WHERE `Id`=12241; -- Destroy the Sapling
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thank you, $N.  I''ll take those from you.$B$BThe corruptive power of these seeds is dangerous.  I must destroy them right away.' WHERE `Id`=12242; -- Vordrassil's Seeds
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Those are the juiciest mana berries I''ve ever seen.  I think I''m getting smarter just by looking at them.$b$bSince I no longer need most of my meat and fish stock, why don''t you take some?  I''m certain you could make something delicious.' WHERE `Id`=11380; -- Manalicious
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can already feel their defenses weakening!$b$bNot since the onset of this conflict have we dealt a blow of this magnitude to the Lord of Magic.$b$bDo not forget to visit Eregos'' cache. Surely some of his treasures will interest you.' WHERE `Id`=13128; -- A Wing and a Prayer
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It''s about time that you arrived.$B$BMehlisah said that she would be sending help days ago.  And we''ve been fighting in here longer than that!' WHERE `Id`=29642; -- Trouble at Auchindoun
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape,  Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE `Id`=14108; -- Get Kraken!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Great job, Champion.  The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE `Id`=14136; -- Rescue at Sea
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE `Id`=14105; -- Deathspeaker Kharos
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Yarzill whispers.>$B$BYou are doing the Netherwing a great service, $N. Slowly, we will topple the Dragonmaw. From the inside a disease now grows - a disease with no cure...$B$BReturn to me tomorrow if you are interested in more work at the Dragonmaw Skyway.
' WHERE `Id`=11035; -- The Not-So-Friendly Skies...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The reflection of the everfrost sparkles in Calder''s eye as he holds it aloft.>$b$bAhh, everfrost. The symbol of the heart of our people...$b$bEverfrost was once plentiful in this region. Over the ages, though, the jormungar have devoured nearly all of it. It is now very rare and very precious to my people.$b$bAs you roam these lands, keep a lookout for more pieces of everfrost. Return to me with any that you find and we will be most grateful.' WHERE `Id`=13420; -- Everfrost
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well done, little $c.$b$bEverfrost was once plentiful in this region. Over the ages, though, the jormungar devoured nearly all of it. It is now very rare and very precious to my people.$b$bAs you roam these lands, keep a lookout for more pieces of everfrost. Return to me with any that you find and we will be most grateful.' WHERE `Id`=13421; -- Remember Everfrost!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Where did you find such a wonderful blade?$B$BThis is a work of astounding craftsmanship and worthy weapon for any champion. I would love to have it for display.$B$BWould you accept a generous number of Darkmoon Faire tickets in trade?' WHERE `Id`=29446; -- A Wondrous Weapon
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Where did you find this collection of runes? I haven''t seen anything like this in years. It''ll be a splendid mystery to unravel!$B$BWould you trade these for Darkmoon tickets?' WHERE `Id`=29464; -- Tools of Divination
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I don''t know how you got your hands on this, and I know better than to ask. Could I convince you to part with it in exchange for Darkmoon tickets?' WHERE `Id`=29451; -- The Master Strategist
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Let us begin, mortal.$b$bThere is little time to spare.' WHERE `Id`=29452; -- Your Time Has Come
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It is no whimsical dalliance that brings you here, mortal.$b$bMuster every fiber of your courage for what you are about to behold.' WHERE `Id`=29129; -- A Legendary Engagement
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Now, $r, you know the reasoning behind your summons.' WHERE `Id`=29134; -- A Wrinkle in Time
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have come seeking my council, mortal. This I know, but do you know what it is that you face?$B$B<Alexstrasza points northward.>$B$BNorth of here are the dying grounds of Galakrond - progenitor of dragonkind. It is from Galakrond that the Titans created the Aspects. Imagine, then, the power of Galakrond. His size alone was greater than all of the Aspects combined! Now attempt to understand what the Scourge do in the Great Dragonblight.$B$BFrost wyrms, mortal, should be the least of your concerns.
' WHERE `Id`=12496; -- Audience With The Dragon Queen
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Greetings to you, $c. I am glad to hear that Ubungo found someone that he could trust.$B$BWelcome to Zim''Torga.' WHERE `Id`=12623; -- To the Witch Doctor
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Zim''Torga''s thoughts pervade your own. She senses the offerings you are about give to her and is pleased.>$B$B<She conveys that you will be appropriately rewarded.>' WHERE `Id`=12615; -- The Blessing of Zim'Torga
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, yes, that''s a good start.$b$bShould I call upon you to help me with an actual recipe, you''ll need to locate ingredients in a timely manner.$b$bKeep that in mind, $c.$b$bFarewell.' WHERE `Id`=12557; -- Lab Work
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is a fine weapon that will help me crush the competition. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `Id`=13769; -- A Worthy Weapon
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is astounding!  Not only have you brought back Medivh''s Journal, but you''ve also retrieved a fragment of his very essence.$B$BAs faint as this lingering essence is, it will reveal to us vital information about Medivh.  We will not forget this, $c.' WHERE `Id`=9644; -- Nightbane
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That is a fine batch of spiritual soup if I ever did smell one.  Just a pinch of pepper and it''s done.$b$bAs promised, here''s your cut.  And because you did such a fine job, I''m going to throw in some of my extra stock.' WHERE `Id`=11381; -- Soup for the Soul
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I knew it!$b$bEven my going missing wasn''t enough to get those spineless weasels to come in here after me.$b$bWell, they sent you. We''ll have to get through this together.' WHERE `Id`=12037; -- Search and Rescue
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ya done it?! Dey be no more?$b$bHere ya go, mon. Take dis gift for bringin'' justice to da frozen wastes.' WHERE `Id`=29834; -- Gal'darah Must Pay
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Amazin''! Dis be like nothing I''ve ever seer before.$B$BGood work, mon.' WHERE `Id`=29839; -- One of a Kind
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We trolls been subject to da splittin'' of empires for longer than some races been existin''.$B$BWe always regrow from da ruins.' WHERE `Id`=29844; -- For Posterity
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Synipus whistles.>$b$bOh, she''s a beauty! We''ll fix her up nice.$b$bIf you''re short on things to do, go talk to Gordun and get a ride down to Venture Bay. They''re sure to need a hand.$b$bOh, and while you''re there, use these keys on a Refurbished Shredder. Wait ''til ya see what these babies can do when they''re cleaned up!' WHERE `Id`=12244; -- Shredder Repair
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well done, $n.$b$bYou''ve bought us some time here, though likely no more than a day. Nevertheless, the Alliance is grateful for your efforts.' WHERE `Id`=12289; -- Kick 'Em While They're Down
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes indeed. These should do the trick...$b$bThere. One more shredder ready for the fight. Thanks, $n.' WHERE `Id`=12268; -- Pieces Parts
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Wonderful!$b$bThe Alliance shall live to see another day, in part due to your diligence.$b$bPlease accept my thanks, friend.' WHERE `Id`=12296; -- Life or Death
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I''m in your debt, mon.  Take this as payment.' WHERE `Id`=12176; -- A Minor Substitution
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''re back.  And you''re alive.$B$BNow what''s this nonsense about worgen?' WHERE `Id`=12412; -- My Enemy's Friend
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hah!  Is this some sort of joke?$B$BI barely have any use for books I can actually understand.' WHERE `Id`=12423; -- Mikhail's Journal
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Could it be?  The man who wrote this journal feared for his daughters'' lives so he sent them away from Silverbrook.$B$BWe just captured an outcast in the outskirts of town about the same age as the eldest daughter.$B$BListen, $N.  There''s more happening here than meets the eye... we can''t just burn this diary.' WHERE `Id`=12424; -- Gorgonna
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''re going to let me go... just like that?  Listen, I don''t want any trouble with you... these monsters killed my father and took my sister.  I have other things on my mind right now.' WHERE `Id`=12422; -- Tactical Clemency
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I thank you, $N.  Your help is appreciated.' WHERE `Id`=12453; -- Eyes Above
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Not bad, $N.  You might be slightly more useful than I initially thought.' WHERE `Id`=12413; -- Attack on Silverbrook
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That''s dire news indeed!  Well, it would seem I made the right choice in sending you out there to help Weeks.  The last thing that we want is the Shadow Council establishing themselves right on our doorstep!$B$B$N, in recognition of your efforts at Grangol''var Village, I hereby grant you the right to your pick of any of these fine rewards.' WHERE `Id`=10042; -- Kill the Shadow Council!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='These are marvelous. Well done!$B$BHere''s your cut, as promised.' WHERE `Id`=29607; -- Eyes of Desire
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Knowing that Lakka is free means I can cut the rest of my ties to the Sethekk.$B$BPart of me will never forgive myself for Syth''s death, but it had to be done. When I reach Skettis, I will perform the death rites for him.' WHERE `Id`=29605; -- Brother Against Brother
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I may never truly be forgiven for my role in the crimes of the Sethekk, but perhaps by restoring the relics of Terokk to my people, I can begin to redeem myself.' WHERE `Id`=29606; -- Terokk's Legacy
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yeah, I''m sure that you killed all of those bonelashers.  It''s obvious since the captain asked for you to turn in proof on that wanted poster.$B$B<Taela gives you a sarcastic look.>$B$BI''ll take your word for it.  I''m not certain who I angered to pull this duty, but thanks for your efforts on behalf of the Alliance.  Here''s a little something for all of your trouble.' WHERE `Id`=10033; -- Wanted: Bonelashers Dead!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Color me impressed, $c.  Torgos was one of the toughest creatures I know of this side of Nagrand.$B$BWell, I suppose that''s good enough for something from the Allerian Stronghold treasury.  Take your pick.' WHERE `Id`=10035; -- Torgos!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I heard the explosion from here. Not with my ears, but with my heart.$b$bIf the touch of the blessed naaru, A''dal, is not enough to bring the arakkoa to redemption, nothing will be. Those who have not given themselves over to the Light are mere servants of evil.$b$bThey must be destroyed.' WHERE `Id`=10839; -- Veil Skith: Darkstone of Terokk
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You found all my friends!  Now I have someone to play with.  Thank you, $GMister:Miss; $n.  $B$BSince I have kids to play with maybe you would like one of my toys?  That way you have something to play with too.' WHERE `Id`=10852; -- Missing Friends
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can breathe a sigh of relief for now, $N.  The Shadow Council will be held off for the time being.$B$BThey are murderers and cowards and your display of courage will keep them at bay.' WHERE `Id`=10878; -- Before Darkness Falls
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Those foul spirits deserved to die. The death they would have wrought on others is reason enough.$b$bWe cannot hope to redeem those in Terokk''s grasp. But we shall deliver them a devastating blow in the name of the Light.' WHERE `Id`=10848; -- Veil Rhaze: Unliving Evil
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I''m sure you are up to the task I have for you if you''ve made it this far in one piece.$B$B<Mayara Brightwing lowers her voice to a whisper.>$B$BBetween you and me, you may want to enjoy yourself in the Grim Guzzler while you''re there. It could be the last drink you ever have.' WHERE `Id`=27569; -- Dark Iron Tacticians
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The Dark Irons took our Thunderbrew. I''ll never let them live after that. I''d kill ''em all myself if I could!$B$BHowever, look ahead and you''ll see we have slightly more dire matters to attend to at the moment.' WHERE `Id`=27571; -- The Grim Guzzler
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I cannot proceed any further alone, regardless of my combat experience. The Lyceum has proven too difficult for me. If you are here, though...you might be the key to all of this.' WHERE `Id`=27573; -- The Dark Iron Pact
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve done well in defeating Binder Murdis, but the Iron Dwarves won''t give up easily.$B$BAs my people move north, I''m certain we will encounter the Iron Dwarves again. Next time, we will be prepared to thwart them before they can dig in.' WHERE `Id`=11352; -- The Rune of Command
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Edan listens as you describe your findings.>$B$BMegalith? A literal transcription from the tablet! This Megalith must be the centerpiece of the iron ones'' mysterious plans.' WHERE `Id`=11366; -- The Lodestone
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve done well in felling Megalith, but I wonder about his final words.$B$BYou''re sure he said the Stoneforge?$B$BIt is not a name our people know, but it sounds like it might be a creation of the \"titans\" the ousiders speak of. The Iron Dwarves have ever been a cunning and dangerous foe, $N. We must watch these giants and find this Stoneforge before they can carry out their plans.' WHERE `Id`=11367; -- Demolishing Megalith
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Garwal was not a worg at all! I know of these creatures... they are called worgen.$B$BBut, Ulfang indicated that it came south from the Grizzly Hills? Odd. There aren''t any worgen there.$B$BI thank you for helping to restore Ulfang to his proper place amongst his pack. Now we both will be able to sleep peacefully.$B$BPlease, you must accept this as a sign of gratitude.' WHERE `Id`=11324; -- Alpha Worg
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Have you done that before? Your skill with my machete seemed practiced.$B$B<The brave looks at you warily.>$B$BI''ll take it back from you now, $c.' WHERE `Id`=11257; -- Gruesome, But Necessary
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The brave nods at you in clear approval of your handling of the torch>$B$BLet these vrykul feel the heat of the land. Let them know the fear they would instill in others!' WHERE `Id`=11258; -- Burn Skorn, Burn!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have a strong arm, $N.$B$BIt looks as if those wind riders finally made themselves useful instead of just standing around and drinking all day.' WHERE `Id`=11259; -- Towers of Certain Doom
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That is good news indeed! You have given us some breathing room to further our preparations for leaving.$B$BPlease, take one of these as a sign of our appreciation.' WHERE `Id`=11261; -- The Conqueror of Skorn!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have my thanks, $N. I know that you do not have any duty to me or my people.$B$BWhat you say about that place troubles me still, and I sense that our culling is not quite at an end.' WHERE `Id`=11263; -- Dealing With Gjalerbron
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A great stone is lifted from my shoulders to hear of your success. And I smile to know that some you freed were taunka.$B$BPlease, take this as a gift for what you have done. I shall see to the health of those you freed.' WHERE `Id`=11265; -- Of Keys and Cages
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The greatmother nods her approval of your actions.>$B$BThank you, $N, you have done what is right and you have bought us a little more time to finish our preparations for leaving. We will soon make the journey north.$B$BI am too old; when we go, I will not be able to carry everything with me. Would you like to take one of these?' WHERE `Id`=11268; -- The Walking Dead
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I''m not sure that I like the sound of that one bit! The Lich King absconding with Ymiron can only mean trouble. Unfortunate that you weren''t able to kill him along with his queen.$B$BStill, you''ve put a huge dent in their plans and bought us the valuable time that we need.$B$BAnd who knows, with the way you get around, you''ll likely run into King Ymiron again. I''m sure that he won''t fare so well the next time you meet.' WHERE `Id`=11453; -- The Slumbering King
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Chieftain Ashtotem breathes a sigh of relief.>$B$BThat should take some of the pressure off.$B$B$N, time and again you have proven your value to the taunka of Camp Winterhoof. Please, choose something from our bounty. I insist.' WHERE `Id`=11264; -- Necro Overlord Mezhen
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You did what had to be done. The unwise might consider it dishonorable to slay the helpless while they awaken, but in this case you would have been a fool to have done otherwise.$B$BAnd we certainly couldn''t have just left them standing there to be ritually wakened, now could we?$B$BIt was a brave thing you did for all of us down in those catacombs, $r.' WHERE `Id`=11433; -- Sleeping Giants
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I''m glad you''ve proven you can follow orders.  If I had a copper piece for every arrogant fool in shiny armor to come here and think they''re above the chain of command... well, I''d have a few gold.$B$BNow that you''ve demonstrated a measure of discipline, I have other tasks more suitable for someone of your caliber.' WHERE `Id`=11270; -- War is Hell
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Did you hunt down some crows, boy?  Good boy, good boy!$B$BAh, these hounds remind me of my days raising purebreds in Tirisfal... those were good times!' WHERE `Id`=11227; -- Let Them Eat Crow
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Cannons are holding us back?  I''ll show them cannons.' WHERE `Id`=11221; -- Reports from the Field
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I hope you''re ready to fight, $N.  The Queen''s fleet needs you!' WHERE `Id`=11229; -- The Windrunner Fleet
