UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I bet the pale whelp felt that!$B$BThat''s one more step towards yer judgment day, Arthas!' WHERE `Id`=29803; -- Ears of the Lich King
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Aye, the hawks are very territorial and often travel in packs. I suppose I could have told you that before I sent you out into the field.
' WHERE `Id`=11468; -- Falcon Versus Hawk
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Bravo, $N! Bravo! The bond of kinship between you and your falcon is strong! Perhaps you can run some reconnaissance missions against the vrykul in the not-too-distant future?' WHERE `Id`=11470; -- There Exists No Honor Among Birds
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''re almost ready to take this work of art into the field, $N!
' WHERE `Id`=11485; -- Iron Rune Constructs and You: Rocket Jumping
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work, $N. I''ll see that these are, ah, disposed of immediately.$B$BAfter all, what would our fine apothecaries want with an army of monstrous, poison-spitting, flesh-eating super-toads?' WHERE `Id`=29319; -- Tadpole Terror
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='So Boktar received my note? That''s excellent news. I doubted the taunka longrunner who carried it would reach anyone.' WHERE `Id`=13426; -- Xarantaur, the Witness
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The chieftain''s spirit told you to bring this to me?$B$B<Xarantaur examines the totem.>$B$BAh, I see what he intended. By telling you to use this totem to close the rifts in the deep, he has given us a clue as to what''s happening to the timeline. A wise chieftain, this Swiftspear, watching over his people even in death.' WHERE `Id`=13038; -- Distortions in Time
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Xarantaur accepts the Lorehammer from you.>$B$BAt last, we''ve pinpointed the time of Stormhoof in history. With this knowledge, we can restore the timeline.' WHERE `Id`=13048; -- Where Time Went Wrong
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We are fortunate that you have recovered these intact, $N. With them, I can use the Lorehammer to send you back in time, to where the North Wind started to corrupt the true timeline. It''s the only way we can restore the true history of this place.' WHERE `Id`=13049; -- The Hero's Arms
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Congratulations are in order, $N. You have bested your challenger and earned the right to advance to the rank of valiant.' WHERE `Id`=13680; -- The Aspirant's Challenge
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Are you ready to get to work, $r?  I think I''ve got the perfect task for you.' WHERE `Id`=9913; -- The Consortium Needs You!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You saw a nest, with hatchlings? Hmm... so our \"he\" is actually a \"she,\" eh?$B$BI guess that settles it. I suppose I wouldn''t want to move a nest full of hatchlings just because of a new neighbor, either.$B$B<Gil favors Trapper Jethan with a mock glare.>$B$BI''m sure we''d get along just fine if ol'' Jethan would stop trying to make a trophy of her.' WHERE `Id`=11418; -- We Call Him Steelfeather
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Welcome to Dalaran! This inn is part of the Silver Enclave, the headquarters of the official Alliance presence in our city.$B$BDon''t forget to bind your hearthstone here for easy travel to the city and access to the portal to Stormwind next door.' WHERE `Id`=29608; -- Allies in Dalaran
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You gave our defenders the extra support they needed, $N. Morale is higher than ever now, thanks to you. I think they''ll be able to handle the remaining onslaught on their own. I''ve got bigger plans for you...' WHERE `Id`=11243; -- If Valgarde Falls...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve done well, mate. Now that we''ve secured the tablets we can try and save Daegarn''s life and recover the cipher that will help us decode the meaning behind these ancient relics!$B$BI''ll hold on to these tablets, you rescue Daegarn.

' WHERE `Id`=11277; -- The Depths of Depravity
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yep. You found me. Woopedy-do!$B$BAnd no, I don''t have the cipher. My beard was the first thing those beasts checked! Oluf''s the one that''s got it now. He''s the chieftain of the gladiators.' WHERE `Id`=11299; -- The Ring of Judgement
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Fascinating tale! Something is actually judgin'' these things? To what end?! For what purpose?$B$BWell, never mind that nonsense. Someone else can figure out that stuff. We got the cipher and the tablets back - and only two fatalities in the whole ordeal.' WHERE `Id`=11300; -- Stunning Defeat at the Ring
