' WHERE `Id`=11429; -- Drop It then Rock It!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work, $N! You took out a good chunk of their dragon riders and really pissed off their leadership.$B$BAre you ready to head back to Valgarde and report the good news to Zorek? If so, I''ve got a crazy idea!
' WHERE `Id`=11421; -- It Goes to 11...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Stanwad takes the bundle from you and begins sorting the data.>$B$BWow. How many people did you say died to get this information?$B$B<Stanwad shakes his head.>$B$BYou''ll be happy to know that what McSorf and his crew of bumbling imbeciles discovered is an ancient recipe for tundra stew. Did he not notice the icons of common vegetables and the pictograph of a humanoid mouth chompin'' down on said veggies? You don''t need a damned cipher to break this code!' WHERE `Id`=11448; -- The Explorers' League Outpost
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, $N. I can see the bond of companionship forming. She has accepted you as master.' WHERE `Id`=11460; -- Trust is Earned
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good job, $N. That''ll slow down the burial process a little.' WHERE `Id`=11477; -- Out of My Element?
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have proven yourself worthy of the title of champion, $N. You will compete at the tournament''s highest level, riding in the grand melee and crushing the competition under the banner of Silvermoon.' WHERE `Id`=13731; -- The Valiant's Challenge
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I am honored that you have chosen to join our delegation. I know you will make us proud, $N.' WHERE `Id`=13709; -- Valiant Of Thunder Bluff
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I welcome you as a champion of the tournament, $N. As a champion, you will be able to compete for the grand championship of the tournament. You may also choose to become a valiant with another Horde city''s delegation and in time, a champion for that city as well.$B$BAll champions must have the assistance of a squire, $N, and you are no exception. Allow me to appoint one of ours to accompany you in battle. He will proudly carry the banner of any city that has named you a champion.' WHERE `Id`=13740; -- A Champion Rises
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Do not worry, $r.$B$BThe eggs they found were but a fraction of our hidden stores within Azjol-Nerub.$B$BOur mighty kingdom shall be reborn.' WHERE `Id`=29808; -- Don't Forget the Eggs!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<A fierce glow emanantes from all of Azak''s eyes as he stares at the husk.>$b$bIt is DONE!$b$bYour name shall be recorded in the extensive history of our people, $r!' WHERE `Id`=29807; -- Death to the Traitor King
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Do not be alarmed, $N. I am close to you, waiting in the shadows. You''ve done well.$B$BYou must continue the mission here - I am too valuable to risk my life against petty criminals like these.' WHERE `Id`=27842; -- Only the Beginning
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='My employers do not take kindly to traitors.$B$BOn the flip side, they are renown for their kindness towards the loyal! You deserve to be rewarded!' WHERE `Id`=27844; -- Traitors!!!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It''s a shame that he was both a human and a worgen. Had he been a proud orc warrior I''d have liked to charge into battle alongside such a fierce combatant.$B$BWe can speak of ill-fated desires another day. It is time to take what is ours from the enemy.' WHERE `Id`=27848; -- Good Intentions...Poor Execution
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Brilliant! Now all I have to do is finish my work, and my Mayhem Reapers will cause...mayhem...on any Horde front!$B$BAnd there won''t be any Defias knockoffs to steal my profits!' WHERE `Id`=27847; -- Not Quite There
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='COWARD!!! Vanessa VanCleef is a dirty human coward! How dare she flee from battle against the Horde and leave her unworthy subordinate to fight!$B$B<Kagtha composes herself.>$B$BNo matter. Her ship is reward enough. The citizens of Stormwind will bear first hand witness to our awe inspiring power using a ship made in part by the very architect of their city!' WHERE `Id`=27850; -- The Defias Kingpin
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The Flaming Eradicator appears to concentrate.>$B$BI spare your life for your help, $r. Leave now...before I change my...mind.' WHERE `Id`=26899; -- The Enemy of My Enemy
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can hear their cries from here! Maybe this will show them how foolish it is to wish for the return of an Old God.' WHERE `Id`=26892; -- Deep in the Deeps
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is exactly what I need!  A fathom core is an incredible well of information that we will be able to draw much good from.  Whatever the Twilight''s Hammer is up to in there - and believe me when I say it is no good - my comrades and I will now uncover.$B$BYou''ve done well here today; the Earthen Ring looks upon you warmly for assisting us.  You''ve also helped the Horde as a whole, and for that you should be proud.' WHERE `Id`=26891; -- Amongst the Ruins
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The beast is slain. I can feel his dark presence fading away forever.' WHERE `Id`=26888; -- Nightmare of the Deeps
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Welcome to the Darkmoon Faire!  This voucher is good for FIVE, yes, FIVE prize tickets and a free copy the world-renowned Darkmoon Field Guide!$B$BWhen you accumulate prize tickets, you''ll want to speak to me about redeeming them for valuable prizes. This handy field guide will help you to locate and identify items of value to our collectors here at the faire!' WHERE `Id`=7926; -- The Darkmoon Faire
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I knew you could do it, $c!  Here''s your prize.  Enjoy the faire.' WHERE `Id`=29438; -- He Shoots, He Scores!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='An impressive display!$b$bHere''s your reward.' WHERE `Id`=29434; -- Tonk Commander
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I knew you could do it!$B$BWe''ll take any extra rings you might have, and give you your prize ticket.$b$bHave fun!' WHERE `Id`=29455; -- Target: Turtle
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='So you have managed to defeat the gnolls.  It felt good, didn''t it?$b$bHere is your prize.  Enjoy the rest of the Darkmoon Faire!' WHERE `Id`=29463; -- It's Hammer Time
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Serves her right for stealing your man in the first place.' WHERE `Id`=25244; -- What Kind of Name is Candy, Anyway?
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Oops. Well, what goes up must eventually come down.' WHERE `Id`=25214; -- Escape Velocity
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You did it! You did it!$B$BWe''re saved, $N!' WHERE `Id`=25251; -- Final Confrontation
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Lok''tar! Victory, $N!' WHERE `Id`=25265; -- Victory!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The orc continues on in hushed tones.>$B$BI know who sent you. Did he give you something to deliver to me?' WHERE `Id`=25266; -- Warchief's Emissary
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thrall had you deliver this?$B$B<The Warchief takes a step back, visibly shaken.>$B$BI understand the meaning of this all too well, goblin.$B$B<Garrosh points to Gobber.>$B$BThis smelly thing was caught unattended in the city and seems to recognize you.$B$BI have already put others of your kind to work in Azshara. Take it with you when you leave.$B$BFrom this day forward, you and your Bilgewater Cartel will serve the Horde!' WHERE `Id`=25267; -- Message for Garrosh
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Potent enough to exterminate a thousand murlocs! I think I''ll put that on the label. You''ve done well, $N, and great work around here gets rewarded.' WHERE `Id`=26998; -- Iterating Upon Success
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Belmont gets a little nervous and sends some newbie to look for me? Listen, I''ve been staking out the old Ivar cottage from inside this outhouse for three days. Your presence threatens the whole damn operation!$B$BThere''s no time to explain. We have to act now or this mission will be compromised.' WHERE `Id`=27039; -- Dangerous Intentions
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Alas, poor Yorick! I knew her, $N. An assassin of infinite courage...$B$BNow, tell me what''s going on? What did you and Yorick discover?' WHERE `Id`=27045; -- Waiting to Exsanguinate
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Crowley... A gnat. An insect, waiting to be crushed beneath my boot heel.$B$BSo he thinks to rouse the feral worgen of Silverpine? We shall show him and his allies the might of the Forsaken!$B$BBut first we must clean up the mess made by the Warchief''s fleet. Without their aid we may lose this war.' WHERE `Id`=27056; -- Belmont's Report
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This fiasco may go down as one of the biggest embarrassments in the history of naval warfare. How did this happen? Drunk happened. That''s how.' WHERE `Id`=27065; -- The Warchief's Fleet
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Looks as if you really gave those worgen a beating and, in the process, lifted the \"shame haze\" they cast over us. Perhaps the sea dogs will quit drinkin'' now.$B$BWho am I kidding?$B$BHah!' WHERE `Id`=27073; -- Give 'em Hell!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Within these crates are held STEEL THUNDER! With our weaponry returned we might have a chance to redeem ourselves.' WHERE `Id`=27069; -- Steel Thunder
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent! Now to prepare the \"meal.\"' WHERE `Id`=27082; -- Playing Dirty
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Apothecary Wormcrud laughs maniacally.>$B$BWas there ever any doubt? An ettin is no match for science!' WHERE `Id`=27088; -- It's Only Poisonous if You Ingest It
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The root of this evil must be found and destroyed! The Skitterweb matriarch must be nearby. No doubt hiding in the nearby cave!' WHERE `Id`=27095; -- Skitterweb Menace
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You rescued our orcs and killed the Skitterweb matriarch? We owe you a great debt of gratitude. You''ve saved us all from certain execution, $N. I''m sure we can rouse these drunken idiots now.' WHERE `Id`=27094; -- Deeper into Darkness
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Lok''tar, $N! Once the ale wears off my orcs will be ready!' WHERE `Id`=27093; -- Lost in the Darkness
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Sylvanas raises an eyebrow.>$B$BSo the orcs are in order?$B$B<Sylvanas reads the commendation letter.>$B$BRecovered their supplies? Killed a dozen worgen? Toppled an ettin? Freed their soldiers and destroyed the Skitterweb matriarch?$B$BI say this rarely, $N, but I am impressed. Perhaps your ability matches your aspirations. We shall see, for now you will be tested!' WHERE `Id`=27096; -- Orcs are in Order
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I see everything, $N. Through Agatha all is known to me.' WHERE `Id`=27097; -- Rise, Forsaken
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It would seem that Crowley is more formidable than I anticipated. Still, he is a man - flesh and bone - full of secrets. Secrets that I know all about...$B$BYou have served me well, $N. I could use someone of your ability at the Sepulcher. I have a plan to deal with Crowley and his insurgents once and for all. Will you help?' WHERE `Id`=27099; -- No Escape
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Do you now understand the importance of our mission here? Crowley and his Alliance dogs must be stopped!' WHERE `Id`=27098; -- Lordaeron
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The Banshee Queen''s voice invades your thoughts.>$B$BYou have avenged the fallen, $N, but there is more to be done.' WHERE `Id`=27181; -- Excising the Taint
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The Banshee Queen''s words float in your head.>$B$BThis book documents a recent meeting with Ivar Bloodfang. The location mentioned is the Deep Elem Mine. I know of this place. It has only one entrance.$B$BWe shall corner and crush them!' WHERE `Id`=27193; -- Seek and Destroy
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I s''pose we''re to corner them first then crush, eh?' WHERE `Id`=27194; -- Cornered and Crushed!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='WHAT!?$B$B<Sylvanas shrieks.>$B$BCROWLEY!!!!!$B$BBastards. Those were some of our strongest soldiers. I have underestimated Crowley and Bloodfang for the last time. Clearly they are an enemy the likes of which we have never seen - willing to sacrifice their own to set a trap like this... unheard of in Alliance warfare.' WHERE `Id`=27195; -- Nowhere to Run
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I will see to it that these insignias are returned to the Undercity at once. The registrar will place their names in our records so that their sacrifice may never be forgotten.' WHERE `Id`=27180; -- Honor the Dead
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Hatchet''s communication device crackles.>$B$BHatchet here, are they all dead?' WHERE `Id`=27231; -- Reinforcements from Fenris
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done well, $n. Hopefully we can use these to prevent further nightmares.' WHERE `Id`=26873; -- Preemptive Methods
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Your efforts shall not go unnoticed, $n.$b$bThank you for your dedication.' WHERE `Id`=26872; -- Deviate Hides
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can already feel the balance returning! Quick, talk to Muyoh to help him awaken Naralex!' WHERE `Id`=26870; -- Cleansing the Caverns
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A-HA! I knew it! Lesson learned, I suppose. We will not fail again. I will be sure to have some ale on hand at the front lines.' WHERE `Id`=27226; -- Hair of the Dog
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Though you killed a large number of the newly turned worgen, many more are sure to appear. Still, their assault will have softened. Well done, $N!' WHERE `Id`=27232; -- The Waters Run Red...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well if it isn''t $Nnub!$B$BI hope you''re ready for battle, because that''s all you''ll find in this hellhole. We''re at the heart of contested territory and these worgen mongrels won''t give an inch!' WHERE `Id`=27290; -- To Forsaken Forward Command
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='If I could still breathe I''d let out a sigh of relief.$B$BDon''t get too comfortable, though, $N, your mission here has just begun.' WHERE `Id`=27333; -- Losing Ground
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='With this device I will be able to communicate with you in the field. Now to check the rest of our frontline outposts.' WHERE `Id`=27345; -- The F.C.D.
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Belmont takes the wolfsbane from you.>$B$BGood. Now just do as Forward Commander Onslaught commands. Try your best to fit in with the rest of the soldiers. We don''t want the Gilneas Liberation Front to get suspicious.$B$BOh, you didn''t know they were watching us? Right now there are five different worgen spies looking down on our position. Just be calm and follow orders. I''ll let you know when we are ready to proceed.' WHERE `Id`=27342; -- In Time, All Will Be Revealed
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='He''s gone? Did he have the sword?$B$BNah...don''t tell me. Don''t matter no more. Mazoga don''t care.$B$BI''m off now, mon. De consequences of my actions await me. Take whatever I was holdin''... I don''t need it where I''m goin''...' WHERE `Id`=27068; -- Chief Ukorz Sandscalp
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You killed dem? All of dem? And you return alive?$B$BTake what you want off my body, den. It''s mostly curse-free, Mazoga promises.' WHERE `Id`=27071; -- Wrath of the Sandfury
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Wow! I knew I could count on you! Here''s something for your troubles.' WHERE `Id`=27076; -- Breaking and Entering
