UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ah, you are the champion Goldrinn promised! Your eyes don''t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We''ve got our work cut out for us here.$B$BPut aside your differences with the Horde, there''s plenty of danger to go around.$B$BAnd take this: the Fang of Goldrinn will allow you to channel the ancient''s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `Id`=25618; -- Into the Maw!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Dead? Good. They sealed their fate when they threw their lot in with Ragnaros and his kingdom of flame.$B$BLeave their bodies down here to crumble into ash.' WHERE `Id`=25576; -- Rage of the Wolf Ancient
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good, good. I like nothing more than to see the works of our enemy destroyed.' WHERE `Id`=25575; -- Forged of Shadow and Flame
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Great work!$B$BThere was a time when adventurers would collect these cores in order to craft mediocre fire-resistant equipment. But for now, I''m glad just to destroy these fiends once and for all.' WHERE `Id`=25577; -- Crushing the Cores
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is the tome we''ve heard about?$B$B<Jordan hefts the stone slab into his arms and looks it over.>$B$BI see... I guess it''s good that I can read some of the elemental script. I''ll work on translating this. Meanwhile, there''s one final problem to take care of.' WHERE `Id`=25599; -- Cindermaul, the Portal Master
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It is done! We''ll seal this fiery hole up behind us and let the minions of the Twilight''s Hammer discover the corpses we left behind. We couldn''t have done it without you, $N!' WHERE `Id`=25600; -- Forgemaster Pyrendius
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You should''ve seen the battle from here! Bodies were falling off of the cliff! Spectacular!' WHERE `Id`=25352; -- Sweeping the Shelf
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='They''re moving supplies to Hyjal straight from the elemental planes? That explains so much.$B$BYou''ve made Goldrinn proud by sealing that flamegate, $N, but there may be more portals to seal. You should check with the other shrines!' WHERE `Id`=25611; -- Return from the Firelands
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Can this wait, $c? The battle is not going well.$B$BOh, you''re here to help. I hope you don''t mind a little heat...' WHERE `Id`=25630; -- The Fires of Mount Hyjal
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very well, $r. I will help you mortals, even from within my bonds.$B$BBut don''t sicken me by claiming it''s my redemption. I do this for my own ends.$B$B<Blackhorn''s sudden grin is unsettling.>' WHERE `Id`=25404; -- If You're Not Against Us...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very good. Please crush the berries into a pulpy liquid. That''s quite an aroma isn''t it?$B$BNow now, don''t gag. It''s beneath you.' WHERE `Id`=25408; -- Seeds of Their Demise
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The wretched creature before you speaks in a wavering voice, its body broken but briefly animated by Blackhorn''s vile potion.>$B$BYes, master?' WHERE `Id`=25411; -- A New Master
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Dead? Good!$B$BBut it seems there''s still so much to be done... fires to quench... and the soil to heal...$B$BI hope you''ll stay close and help us reclaim Hyjal!' WHERE `Id`=25382; -- Disrupting the Rituals
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thank you, $N. You''ve given us the opportunity to try to reclaim the upper hand.' WHERE `Id`=25381; -- Fighting Fire With ... Anything
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Squueeeee!$B$BDid the nice $gMr.:Mrs.; $c pull you from the flames, little friend? You''re safe now!$B$BHooray!' WHERE `Id`=25385; -- Save the Wee Animals
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, yes! Show me the runes you discovered.$B$B\"Vol''talo Thol''embaar.\" That''s the name of your real enemy.$B$BPresumably you''re dealing with one of Ragnaros''s generals, sent here to scorch the mountainside and pave the way for his conquest.$B$BI will show you how to crush him.' WHERE `Id`=25412; -- The Name Never Spoken
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Oh yay! Happy little deer!$B$BNow they can grow up and have ADVENTURES.$B$BYou''re swell.' WHERE `Id`=25392; -- Oh, Deer!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='There it is! Such a trophy! Born in the fires of another plane...$B$BGo ahead, $r. Crush it. Crush his charcoal heart in your hands and let the winds scatter the ashes... yes, yes.' WHERE `Id`=25428; -- Black Heart of Flame
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='What? Blackhorn helped you combat the inferno but escaped in the process? That crafty weasel!$B$BIt''s not your fault, $N. He''d probably been plotting this the moment he saw the flames begin creeping up the mountain. We''ll have to deal with him later.' WHERE `Id`=29066; -- Good News... and Bad News
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The forest is being devoured!' WHERE `Id`=25940; -- Last Stand at Whistling Grove
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I thank you, $N. Those little bears are shaken up but they''ll survive.$B$BAt least the ones that hit the mat.' WHERE `Id`=25462; -- The Bears Up There
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very good. The Twilight''s Hammer must be sent the message that we will never give up.' WHERE `Id`=25490; -- Smashing Through Ashes
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The Arch Druid inspects the seedlings.>$B$BThese seedlings have survived an apocalypse. Even a handful hold great power. Life always replenishes itself, often stronger than before.$B$BOnce the way is clear, we will use these to perform a miracle on this mountain, $N. You will see.' WHERE `Id`=25491; -- Durable Seeds
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very good. We will need these to act as bait while they are still warm.$B$BHere is my plan...' WHERE `Id`=25493; -- Fresh Bait
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good work, $N. There''s a chance the forest will recover from this yet.$B$BNow, there''s something else I need you to take care of for me...' WHERE `Id`=25492; -- Firebreak
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That''s good! Between your work and the work of a few others, that valley is secure from a counter-attack.$B$BI''ve done all I can. It''s all up to you and the Arch Druid now.' WHERE `Id`=25502; -- Prepping the Soil
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The Arch Druid takes the shell from you with surprising reverence.>$B$BNemesis is an instrument of evil, but he was forged from a shell fragment of the true ancient.$B$BWe will exploit this connection.' WHERE `Id`=25507; -- Hell's Shells
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='$R.$B$BThis tongue. Is not yours.$B$BWhat do you want ... tormentor?' WHERE `Id`=25510; -- Tortolla Speaks
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='$R.$BYou are not like the others.$B$BBraver. Stronger.$BA part of this world...$B    and not the shadow that came before.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `Id`=25519; -- Children of Tortolla
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Tortolla quivers and shakes debris free from his great back.>$B$BYou...$BAre not like the others.$B$BI am free once again.$B$BThe others...$BWill pay.' WHERE `Id`=25514; -- Breaking the Bonds
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='$N!$B$BYou were able to earn the ancient''s trust?$B$BWonderful! We are one step closer to taking back this mountain...' WHERE `Id`=25520; -- An Ancient Awakens
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ysera herself sent you to me? Oh! It''s an honor to speak with a representative of the aspects.$B$BIt''s true that our shrine is in jeopardy. The harpies we once sheltered in our boughs have suddenly turned against us.$B$BBut please, don''t rejoin the fight until you are ready. Our shrine is no mere battleground. Use its peace and power to center yourself.' WHERE `Id`=27874; -- Aviana's Legacy
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The Halls of Reflection lie ahead.$B$BIf what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE `Id`=24712; -- Deliverance from the Pit
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I would stay away from Oralius. Far, far, far away. He isn''t quite right in the head.$B$BNow, let''s get onto business!' WHERE `Id`=27568; -- Infiltrating Shadowforge City
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have successfully stopped Hakkar here, but I fear we are far from done. The Atal''ai transported most of the blood they produced to Zul''Gurub, where the Hakkari work to summon The Blood God there.$B$B$N, I do not think that this was ever meant to be the place of Hakkar''s arrival - it was merely a test to see if the blood was potent enough! Hakkar can only be summoned in Zul''Gurub...and I fear we may be too late to stop the Hakkari with the blood they now have in their possession.' WHERE `Id`=27633; -- The Blood God Hakkar
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent! I suspect that without Jammal''an''s leadership, the trolls will fall to infighting and Hakkar will never set his eyes upon our world.' WHERE `Id`=27604; -- Jammal'an the Prophet
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You only defeated Eranikus'' Shade? This is most troubling...$B$BLet us hope that his full form does not still exist outside the Temple. Only Ysera herself is stronger than him in our flight.' WHERE `Id`=27605; -- Eranikus
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thank goodness you''re here. I''ve discovered the secret of the fierce Winterfall furbolg.' WHERE `Id`=28544; -- Hero's Call: Winterspring!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Zug zug!  My name is Grunth, and I guess you''re looking after me?  You''re an adventurer, like my mom and dad were.  My matron says that they died with honor in battle.  I''m happy to meet you.$B$BI hope we''ll do plenty of things together.  I have some things I''d like to do, and the matron says you''ll be like a big $G brother : sister; to me during this week.  I''d like that a whole bunch.' WHERE `Id`=172; -- Children's Week
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That was great! I even learned how to control the rocket and everything! Did you see how I saved us? I''m gonna be a rocket pilot when I grow up!' WHERE `Id`=29146; -- Ridin' the Rocketway
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Someday, I''m going to be a great warrior, just like Cairne or the warchief. Everyone will remember my deeds, and the ancestors will welcome my spirit too!' WHERE `Id`=29176; -- The Fallen Chieftain
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='She''s just as fierce as I thought she''d be! But that ambassador sure got real mad when I started talking to Lady Sylvanas.' WHERE `Id`=29167; -- The Banshee Queen
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thanks for the kite, $N. Every time I fly it, I''ll remember the day you gave it to me!' WHERE `Id`=29190; -- Let's Go Fly a Kite
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I think that''s the first time I''ve ever seen a goblin making food that didn''t involve a big, noisy machine with a lot of smoke. Maybe more people would like their food if they just made it like normal people... or like mages! That ice cream was so good!' WHERE `Id`=29191; -- You Scream, I Scream...
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='May the spirits bless you, $N.  You''ve done more for Grunth than most would ever think of doing for him.  Thank you - you''re the epitome of what it means to be a hero of the Horde.$B$BThe orphans will love your gift; it''s not often that they get a new toy.$B$BGrunth had so much fun with you, $N.  He wanted to give you one of his favorite pets to remember him by.' WHERE `Id`=5502; -- A Warden of the Horde
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Welcome to your first true test as a tauren.' WHERE `Id`=14449; -- The First Step
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve fought well, $n. We may yet be saved.' WHERE `Id`=14452; -- Rite of Strength
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thanks to you, our people are free to fight for our home.' WHERE `Id`=24852; -- Our Tribe, Imprisoned
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='More trials lay ahead, $n. I hope you''re prepared.' WHERE `Id`=14458; -- Go to Adana
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well done, $n. Respect your prey, and the danger it carries, but never fear it. In fear, you become prey yourself.' WHERE `Id`=14456; -- Rite of Courage
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='With the corruptors slain, the Earth Mother will mend her own wounds in due time.  The roots are not meant to thrive here, and will wither.  Balance will return.' WHERE `Id`=14455; -- Stop the Thorncallers
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Each of us plays a role in our tribe. Each of us must also go through all the same rites. Do not ever let your pride tell you otherwise.$B$BI remain here to train new warriors that seek the glory of battle and who follow the ways of our oldest ancestors. When you feel ready, come back to me and I will do what I can to train you further. Go with the tribe''s blessing, $N.' WHERE `Id`=3091; -- Simple Note
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done well, $N. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `Id`=27020; -- The First Lesson
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good work, $n.  Those beasts could have been a greater threat than the quilboar themselves, if we had not taken action now.' WHERE `Id`=14459; -- The Battleboars
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve not only wiped the boar pens clean, but put a stop to a horrible desecration.  Well done.' WHERE `Id`=14461; -- Feed of Evil
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Chief Hawkwind holds the mane of Thornmantle over his head.>$B$BThe Chief of the Bristleback is slain. Greatmother Hawkwind''s spirit has been avenged!' WHERE `Id`=14460; -- Rite of Honor
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='There is balance in all things. As Greatmother Hawkwind''s spirit takes its final journey, you will begin your first.' WHERE `Id`=24861; -- Last Rites, First Rites
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='If you are prepared to leave Camp Narache behind, I will help call the spirits to guide you onwards.' WHERE `Id`=23733; -- Rites of the Earthmother
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Welcome to Bloodhoof Village, hero.  I am glad the spirits have guided you safely here.' WHERE `Id`=24215; -- Rite of the Winds
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='$N, it is good you''ve taken the task seriously. Respect of the land and its creatures is important. Death and life are a circle... a necessity. One cannot exist without the other. Take time to ponder this and do well to never forget it.' WHERE `Id`=14438; -- Sharing the Land
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done well, $N.  I will take these and bind their power into a totem of cleansing.' WHERE `Id`=20440; -- Poison Water
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I know that gathering these quills was not an easy task, $N.  In doing this, you prove that you are a $c of merit.  It is good to have you at Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE `Id`=761; -- Swoop Hunting
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The Grimtotem...$B$B<Mull scowls.>$B$BI''d hoped to see the end of my days before Tauren attacked other Tauren senselessly on the very plains of Mulgore.  But be proud, $N.  You have done a great thing for the land, and for our people.' WHERE `Id`=24440; -- Winterhoof Cleansing
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The land is clearly still in great upheaval if it took such effort to calm.$B$BRemember this, $n.  Do not forget seeing the fate of those who would scar the Earth Mother.' WHERE `Id`=14491; -- The Restless Earth
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='If you must take these hides to Thunder Bluff, then you have come to the right place.' WHERE `Id`=6361; -- A Bundle of Hides
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thank you, $N.  The purity with which these beasts hunt is vital in the creation of the next cleansing totem.$B$BThe Thunderhorn Well is a symbol of my own tribe, and to know it is being desecrated by our own kind raises a fury in me I haven''t felt for years.' WHERE `Id`=24441; -- Thunderhorn Totem
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It does indeed appear that the Venture Co. is attempting to rob us of our natural resources. It is good to know this is true, and now it seems, we must do something about it.' WHERE `Id`=751; -- The Ravaged Caravan
