UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The loss of life...it pains me.$B$B<Watcher Jhang sighs.>$B$BThank you, $N. When we are all reunited, the naga won''t stand a chance.' WHERE `Id`=29563; -- Lost in Action
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Perhaps now we can restore all of the desperately needed water to the land.' WHERE `Id`=29615; -- Windcaller Claw and the Water Thief
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I wish it had not come to this, but the naga refused all attempts to negotiate.' WHERE `Id`=29613; -- A Proper Fate
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I''m glad we were able to contain this before it spread across all of Zangarmarsh or further. Thank you.' WHERE `Id`=29614; -- Containment is Key
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You''ve done all of Zangarmarsh a favor this day, $N. The spore giants may be naturally aggressive, but they''re still a vital part of the ecosystem.' WHERE `Id`=29568; -- A Necessary Evil
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Soon we''ll all be together again, and I owe it all to you!$B$BWe''ll bring the naga down before you know it, they don''t stand a chance!' WHERE `Id`=29570; -- Rescuing the Expedition
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='These will do nicely, but we can always use more.  Perhaps you will find yourself in the Underbog again soon?' WHERE `Id`=29691; -- Bring Me A Shrubbery!
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The Black Stalker is dead!  Normally I would not revel in such butchery, but the pain that the great mother and her brood have put my people through over the centuries is unspeakable.$B$BYou have my deepest thanks, brave $c.' WHERE `Id`=29567; -- Stalk the Stalker
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You rescued Akuno, a dear friend of mine.  For this I am in your debt, $N.' WHERE `Id`=10887; -- Escaping the Tomb
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The Light might have forgotten me, but I have not forgotten the Light.  These relics were once very sacred to my people.$B$BAllowing the Shadow Council to use their power for evil is... unthinkable!' WHERE `Id`=10881; -- The Shadow Tomb
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done much to help Terokkar Forest, $N.  With the worst of the mite colonies destroyed we may yet be able to reclaim this wasted land.' WHERE `Id`=10896; -- The Infested Protectors
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='On behalf of the tortured souls you have freed, I thank you, $r.' WHERE `Id`=10842; -- Vengeful Souls
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Out here in the wilds of Outland we are weak with few heroes to defend our rights, but you have given them something to fear $c.  I do not think the ethereals will soon forget the strong right arm of $N. ' WHERE `Id`=10840; -- The Tomb of Lights
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It is grim work toiling with someone''s hatchlings, yet ignoring the brewing evil would be a bleak proposition as well. You have done well.  A''dal''s favor shines upon your heart.' WHERE `Id`=10861; -- Veil Lithic: Preemptive Strike
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done that which needed doing and there is nothing to forgive.  Though it saddens me to hear that they were corrupted into a horrible undeath, through your actions you have put them to rest.$B$BThank you for setting them free, $N.  You must accept a humble token of my regard for you and your selflessness.' WHERE `Id`=10031; -- Helping the Lost Find Their Way
